snippet.title: Ztar Attack 3 : F3 2019 TRAILER (DEMO IN DESCRIPTION)
snippet.description:
Special thanks to Biobak_ who did the trailer for me! Check out his work just here : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQH2lYBypWPpudw1lnBCEuQ

You can download the demo just here!
(v1.0)BPS patch : http://www.mediafire.com/file/hyul3isb8hsjobw/Ztar_Attack_3_-_F3_2019_DEMO_%2528bps_patch%2529.zip/file
Pre-patched : http://www.mediafire.com/file/c3kxevdo5g7ty55/Ztar_Attack_3_-_F3_2019_DEMO_%2528Pre-patched%2529.zip/file

This hack is endorsed by SM64_France, a French collective for people who are passionate about Super Mario 64 romhacks! Check out our channel : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCp60Wu4n8MKdyjpf2nTL8Hg
